"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"# Security Best Practices\\n\\n## Wallet Security\\n\\n1. **Secure Storage**: Store provider wallet keys securely\\n2. **Access Control**: Limit access to wallet files\\n3. **Backup**: Keep secure backups of your wallet\\n4. **Rotation**: Consider periodic key rotation\\n\\n## API Security\\n\\n1. **HTTPS Only**: Always use HTTPS for your service endpoints\\n2. **Authentication**: Implement proper authentication if needed\\n3. **Rate Limiting**: Protect against abuse with rate limits\\n4. **Input Validation**: Validate all incoming requests\\n\\n## Network Security\\n\\n1. **Firewall**: Configure firewalls to allow only necessary traffic\\n2. **Monitoring**: Monitor for unusual activity\\n3. **Updates**: Keep all software updated\\n4. **Logging**: Maintain comprehensive logs\\n\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/provider-guide/security#security-best-practices\",\"html\":\"</header>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/provider-guide/security.mdx#security-best-practices\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\n\",\"title\":\"Security Best Practices\",\"titles\":[]},{\"href\":\"/provider-guide/security#wallet-security\",\"html\":\"\\n<ol>\\n<li><strong>Secure Storage</strong>: Store provider wallet keys securely</li>\\n<li><strong>Access Control</strong>: Limit access to wallet files</li>\\n<li><strong>Backup</strong>: Keep secure backups of your wallet</li>\\n<li><strong>Rotation</strong>: Consider periodic key rotation</li>\\n</ol>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/provider-guide/security.mdx#wallet-security\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\\nSecure Storage: Store provider wallet keys securely\\nAccess Control: Limit access to wallet files\\nBackup: Keep secure backups of your wallet\\nRotation: Consider periodic key rotation\\n\\n\",\"title\":\"Wallet Security\",\"titles\":[\"Security Best Practices\"]},{\"href\":\"/provider-guide/security#api-security\",\"html\":\"\\n<ol>\\n<li><strong>HTTPS Only</strong>: Always use HTTPS for your service endpoints</li>\\n<li><strong>Authentication</strong>: Implement proper authentication if needed</li>\\n<li><strong>Rate Limiting</strong>: Protect against abuse with rate limits</li>\\n<li><strong>Input Validation</strong>: Validate all incoming requests</li>\\n</ol>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/provider-guide/security.mdx#api-security\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\\nHTTPS Only: Always use HTTPS for your service endpoints\\nAuthentication: Implement proper authentication if needed\\nRate Limiting: Protect against abuse with rate limits\\nInput Validation: Validate all incoming requests\\n\\n\",\"title\":\"API Security\",\"titles\":[\"Security Best Practices\"]},{\"href\":\"/provider-guide/security#network-security\",\"html\":\"\\n<ol>\\n<li><strong>Firewall</strong>: Configure firewalls to allow only necessary traffic</li>\\n<li><strong>Monitoring</strong>: Monitor for unusual activity</li>\\n<li><strong>Updates</strong>: Keep all software updated</li>\\n<li><strong>Logging</strong>: Maintain comprehensive logs</li>\\n</ol>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/provider-guide/security.mdx#network-security\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\\nFirewall: Configure firewalls to allow only necessary traffic\\nMonitoring: Monitor for unusual activity\\nUpdates: Keep all software updated\\nLogging: Maintain comprehensive logs\\n\",\"title\":\"Network Security\",\"titles\":[\"Security Best Practices\"]}]}}"
